  stimulus_text = 'Although he had visited Paris many times, the artist had never been to the Louvre, *the most famous museum in the world*.  He had always been drawn to smaller, more intimate galleries, where the crowds were less overwhelming, and the artwork was more approachable.  The artist, however, decided to make a special trip to the Louvre *when his last visit to Paris*.  He was *excited to see* the Mona Lisa and to experience the museum’s vast collection of art.',
